{"tid":2171054,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚憎聽到人話「網上都係一樣咁做嘅啫」","createTime":"2020-08-23T16:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T07:22:51.000Z","uid":367224,"like":19,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a70aa82f3187684a21dad04fe05ebcdce780d513","tid":2171054,"uid":367224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:33:14.000Z","msg":"fm嚟緊要用zoom上堂好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日喺屋企冇心機冇動力做嘢 考完dse之後已經冇再學過嘢<br />\n喺屋企對住兩件公屋廢老嘅時間多咗 淨係處理同屋企人嘅關係已經好攰<br />\n<br />\n以前喺學校淨係讀書 返屋企就淨係玩/休息<br />\n靠住呢個規律都叫考到個唔錯嘅成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家冇咗規律 開cam又令我覺得自己嘅私人空間受侵犯 連唯一一個唔使講嘢/見人嘅空間都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政治+疫情又搞到成個社會氣氛好壓抑 出街戴住口罩又唔舒服 好似揾唔到放鬆嘅空間<br />\n但係見好多人都覺得疫情對讀書冇乜影響 我讀得差嘅話又好似揾藉口咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b896ba7117b1b0e43634188457d5af50fe2c8b","tid":2171054,"uid":8308,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"讀U要係屋企上ZOOM真係好慘<br />\n讀U就係貪佢有得住宿 上完堂瘋狂去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03f13e81a61f23f692a3f0d12cd538d77190f06","tid":2171054,"uid":367224,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"同埋網上識人真係難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔住個moon嗰種唔自然同距離感好難講清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f50e1001dec70015f27b0bbcc07549b1c3adaea","tid":2171054,"uid":118217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:37:56.000Z","msg":"好明顯佢唔識"},{"pid":"45f2e9ebb06c92ed02feaed162104028173b9b6f","tid":2171054,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji